<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>恋爱小日记</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", sans-serif;
  height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce4ec 0%, #f8f0e6 50%, #fff8e1 100%);
  overflow: hidden;
}
.home-card {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 60px 40px;
}
.home-icon { font-size: 64px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.home-title {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #2d2a24;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.home-subtitle {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #8a857e;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.home-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 16px 48px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 50px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8686c, #d4585c);
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(232,104,108,0.3);
  text-decoration: none;
}
.home-btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(232,104,108,0.4);
}
.home-btn:active {
  transform: translateY(0);
}
.home-hearts {
  font-size: 20px;
  margin-top: 32px;
  color: #e8686c;
  opacity: 0.6;
  letter-spacing: 8px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="home-card">
  <div class="home-icon">💌</div>
  <div class="home-title">噢一次 &amp; 噢零次</div>
  <div class="home-subtitle">我们的恋爱小日记</div>
  <a href="/write" class="home-btn">
    进入
    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
  </a>
  <div class="home-hearts">
    <div class="copyright" style="margin-top:16px;font-size:12px;color:#8a857e;letter-spacing:0">u00A9 2026 Jim</div>♥ ♥ ♥</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
